{"tid":1329650,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］［廣傳］民政局私底下約中學生閉門密會_2","createTime":"2019-07-18T09:28:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T01:24:16.000Z","uid":28444,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"7cfe74d0521571ba559e59a30a4d1b3b5637f949","tid":1329650,"uid":28444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T09:28:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>代教育社福界手足出post：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">事件好緊急，如果俾佢搞得成，政府就可以話已經接觸青年，玩屈民意呢招。<br />\n而班年輕人就會被擺上檯做箭靶</span></span><br />\n<br />\n話說前日(15/7)有個自稱民政局C小姐嘅人(驚淨係得佢一對一聯絡我地個學生，為保護學生所以唔出名)聯絡我地學校嘅學生，大致意思係要佢參加今個星期五民政局搞嘅gathering。<br />\n<br />\n屆時有機會見到張建宗或者柒婆，同埋一啲「制定中央政策相關的官員」，另外同場會有大概1X個青年大使。<br />\n<br />\n話個會面係好臨時決定，應該係14-15/7先決定。又冇交代過目的係咩，淨係話想學生「發表自己意見」。又強調屆時唔會安排記者出席。<br />\n<br />\n我個學生好驚中伏俾班官利用所以搵我地幫手，我地先知有單咁嘅嘢，但係網上搵唔到相關嘅資料。<br />\n<br />\n聚會資料如下：<br />\n日期：2019-7-19<br />\n時間：16:30-18:00<br />\n(請早十分鐘到訪客入口處登記入閘，即香港添馬添美道2號政府總部東翼 二樓職員入口處)<br />\n地點: 香港添馬添美道2號政府總部西翼 26樓 政策創新與統籌辦事處 多功能場地(Multi-function Area, PICO)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">屌你班高官龜縮咁撚多日擺晒班警犬出黎咬人都未算，宜家諗住推班細路出黎擋，全部仆街死啦你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n麻煩大家將單嘢廣傳開去，公開柒婆啲賤招，等班細路唔洗受靶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n［突發］［廣傳］民政局私底下約中學生閉門密會<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dkchkT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dkchkT</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>請熱烈到場支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"de7687a97d6b1b597fd731e0054eb59cae62c177","tid":1329650,"uid":11719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T09:28:47.000Z","msg":"洗腦"},{"pid":"ca5fcef3637f19ed6164cf0b8633bb1fe7047f71","tid":1329650,"uid":28444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T09:31:31.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請熱烈到場支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"bf80464957f20e0d2597f4a0ac78d12eca40017a","tid":1329650,"uid":28444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T09:33:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">林奠唔好搞中學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"881323323376f67dbc981ef760785b302b8e9831","tid":1329650,"uid":28444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T09:39:07.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請熱烈到場支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"b6a1e45b9024aab1e32c1c7eb11cb234df7f5bb1","tid":1329650,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T09:40:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c70f1bd54acd2199f0af4f330d006f303ffe45c3","tid":1329650,"uid":28444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T09:41:01.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請熱烈到場支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"d91199fa588eb4d5223f957520c22cd4a28651ff","tid":1329650,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T09:45:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5ec0b52f72ef2903769d6551955577fc3b7ee058","tid":1329650,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T09:55:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c78a35ff9dcf6bbbaf45a94accdc9587dbcccb11","tid":1329650,"uid":28444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T10:00:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"140343340ec33e0a3f6e1b89f9c933e46d2b0557","tid":1329650,"uid":28444,"like":0,"disli